    "python": "Pin CPython 3.12 as Orkas' conservative skill/runtime baseline for broad third-party wheel compatibility. 3.12.13 is the Python.org 3.12 security release available in python-build-standalone 20260610. Move to a newer Python minor only after package smoke tests pass on macOS, Windows, and Linux.",
