    "node": "Pin Node.js 24.x Active LTS as the baseline for Node-based skills/packages (bash `node`/`npm`/`npx` and orkas-pkg `npm install`). Newest LTS chosen so libraries requiring high node versions are covered; official nodejs.org binaries bundle npm/npx. 24.17.0 was the latest v24 LTS on nodejs.org dist/latest-v24.x checked on 2026-06-22. Libraries needing an even newer major are out of scope for the built-in single version. Move only after package install/run smoke tests pass on macOS and Windows.",
